        SELECT [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID] AS [WsproductSecondGroupId], [w0].[SGName] AS [Sgname], REPLACE([w0].[EnSgname], N' ', N'-') AS [EnSgname], [w0].[FirstGroupId]

""SELECT [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId], [p].[Name], [p].[UrlName], [p].[Icon], [t0].[PrdFirstGroupID], [t0].[FGName], [t0].[EnFgname], [t0].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t0].[Sgname], [t0].[EnSgname]
FROM [ParsaPooladMenus] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [w].[PrdFirstGroupID], [w].[FGName], [w].[EnFgname], [t].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t].[Sgname], [t].[EnSgname], [w].[ParsaPooladMenusId]
    FROM [WSProductFirstGroup] AS [w]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID] AS [WsproductSecondGroupId], [w0].[SGName] AS [Sgname], REPLACE([w0].[EnSgname], N' ', N'-') AS [EnSgname], [w0].[FirstGroupId]

        WHERE [w0].[IsRemoved] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [w].[PrdFirstGroupID] = [t].[FirstGroupId]
    WHERE [w].[IsRemoved] IS NULL
) AS [t0] ON [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId] = [t0].[ParsaPooladMenusId]
ORDER BY [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId], [t0].[PrdFirstGroupID], [t0].[WsproductSecondGroupId]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId], [p].[Name], [p].[UrlName], [p].[Icon], [t0].[PrdFirstGroupID], [t0].[FGName], [t0].[EnFgname], [t0].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t0].[Sgname], [t0].[EnSgname]
FROM [ParsaPooladMenus] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [w].[PrdFirstGroupID], [w].[FGName], [w].[EnFgname], [t].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t].[Sgname], [t].[EnSgname], [w].[ParsaPooladMenusId]
    FROM [WSProductFirstGroup] AS [w]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID] AS [WsproductSecondGroupId], [w0].[SGName] AS [Sgname], REPLACE([w0].[EnSgname], N' ', N'-') AS [EnSgname], [w0].[FirstGroupId]

        WHERE [w0].[IsRemoved] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [w].[PrdFirstGroupID] = [t].[FirstGroupId]
    WHERE [w].[IsRemoved] IS NULL
) AS [t0] ON [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId] = [t0].[ParsaPooladMenusId]
ORDER BY [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId], [t0].[PrdFirstGroupID], [t0].[WsproductSecondGroupId]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Author], [t].[BlogCategoryId], [t].[Body], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[InsertTime], [t].[IsRemoved], [t].[IsVerified], [t].[IsVideoClip], [t].[LocalTime], [t].[Position], [t].[RegisterUserId], [t].[RemoveTime], [t].[RequestToAuthorFav], [t].[Slug], [t].[SmallDescription], [t].[Title], [t].[UpdateTime], [t].[VideoClipDuration], [t].[VisitCount], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Color], [t0].[FaIcon], [t0].[ImageUrl], [t0].[InsertTime], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsRemoved], [t0].[LocalTime], [t0].[Name], [t0].[RegisterUserId], [t0].[RemoveTime], [t0].[Slug], [t0].[SmallDescription], [t0].[UpdateTime]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [b].[Id], [b].[Author], [b].[BlogCategoryId], [b].[Body], [b].[ImageUrl], [b].[InsertTime], [b].[IsRemoved], [b].[IsVerified], [b].[IsVideoClip], [b].[LocalTime], [b].[Position], [b].[RegisterUserId], [b].[RemoveTime], [b].[RequestToAuthorFav], [b].[Slug], [b].[SmallDescription], [b].[Title], [b].[UpdateTime], [b].[VideoClipDuration], [b].[VisitCount]

    SELECT [w].[PrdFirstGroupID], [w].[FGName], [w].[EnFgname], [t].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t].[Sgname], [t].[EnSgname], [w].[ParsaPooladMenusId]
    FROM [WSProductFirstGroup] AS [w]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID] AS [WsproductSecondGroupId], [w0].[SGName] AS [Sgname], REPLACE([w0].[EnSgname], N' ', N'-') AS [EnSgname], [w0].[FirstGroupId]

2021-08-14T10:50:17.3401493+04:30 0HMAUSHFRNJVO:0000012D [INF] Executed DbCommand ("8"ms) [Parameters=["@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)"], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']"
""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Color], [t].[FaIcon], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[InsertTime], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsRemoved], [t].[LocalTime], [t].[Name], [t].[RegisterUserId], [t].[RemoveTime], [t].[Slug], [t].[SmallDescription], [t].[UpdateTime], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Author], [t0].[BlogCategoryId], [t0].[Body], [t0].[ImageUrl], [t0].[InsertTime], [t0].[IsRemoved], [t0].[IsVerified], [t0].[IsVideoClip], [t0].[LocalTime], [t0].[Position], [t0].[RegisterUserId], [t0].[RemoveTime], [t0].[RequestToAuthorFav], [t0].[Slug], [t0].[SmallDescription], [t0].[Title], [t0].[UpdateTime], [t0].[VideoClipDuration], [t0].[VisitCount]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [b0].[Id], [b0].[Color], [b0].[FaIcon], [b0].[ImageUrl], [b0].[InsertTime], [b0].[IsActive], [b0].[IsRemoved], [b0].[LocalTime], [b0].[Name], [b0].[RegisterUserId], [b0].[RemoveTime], [b0].[Slug], [b0].[SmallDescription], [b0].[UpdateTime], (
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([b].[VisitCount]), 0)
        FROM [dbo].[Blogs] AS [b]
        WHERE ([b].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([b0].[Id] = [b].[BlogCategoryId])) AS [c]
    FROM [dbo].[BlogCategories] AS [b0]
    WHERE [b0].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
    ORDER BY (
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([b].[VisitCount]), 0)
        FROM [dbo].[Blogs] AS [b]
        WHERE ([b].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([b0].[Id] = [b].[BlogCategoryId])) DESC
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b1].[Id], [b1].[Author], [b1].[BlogCategoryId], [b1].[Body], [b1].[ImageUrl], [b1].[InsertTime], [b1].[IsRemoved], [b1].[IsVerified], [b1].[IsVideoClip], [b1].[LocalTime], [b1].[Position], [b1].[RegisterUserId], [b1].[RemoveTime], [b1].[RequestToAuthorFav], [b1].[Slug], [b1].[SmallDescription], [b1].[Title], [b1].[UpdateTime], [b1].[VideoClipDuration], [b1].[VisitCount]
    FROM [dbo].[Blogs] AS [b1]
    WHERE [b1].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[BlogCategoryId]
ORDER BY [t].[c] DESC, [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId], [p].[Name], [p].[UrlName], [p].[Image], [t0].[PrdFirstGroupID], [t0].[FGName], [t0].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t0].[Sgname]
FROM [ParsaPooladMenus] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [w].[PrdFirstGroupID], [w].[FGName], [t].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t].[Sgname], [w].[ParsaPooladMenusId]
    FROM [WSProductFirstGroup] AS [w]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID] AS [WsproductSecondGroupId], [w0].[SGName] AS [Sgname], [w0].[FirstGroupId]

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Color], [t].[FaIcon], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[InsertTime], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsRemoved], [t].[LocalTime], [t].[Name], [t].[RegisterUserId], [t].[RemoveTime], [t].[Slug], [t].[SmallDescription], [t].[UpdateTime], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Author], [t0].[BlogCategoryId], [t0].[Body], [t0].[ImageUrl], [t0].[InsertTime], [t0].[IsRemoved], [t0].[IsVerified], [t0].[IsVideoClip], [t0].[LocalTime], [t0].[Position], [t0].[RegisterUserId], [t0].[RemoveTime], [t0].[RequestToAuthorFav], [t0].[Slug], [t0].[SmallDescription], [t0].[Title], [t0].[UpdateTime], [t0].[VideoClipDuration], [t0].[VisitCount]

    FROM [dbo].[Blogs] AS [b1]
    WHERE [b1].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[BlogCategoryId]

        SELECT [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID] AS [WsproductSecondGroupId], [w0].[SGName] AS [Sgname], REPLACE([w0].[EnSgname], N' ', N'-') AS [EnSgname], [w0].[FirstGroupId]

""SELECT [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId], [p].[Name], [p].[UrlName], [p].[Image], [t0].[PrdFirstGroupID], [t0].[FGName], [t0].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t0].[Sgname]
FROM [ParsaPooladMenus] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [w].[PrdFirstGroupID], [w].[FGName], [t].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t].[Sgname], [w].[ParsaPooladMenusId]
    FROM [WSProductFirstGroup] AS [w]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID] AS [WsproductSecondGroupId], [w0].[SGName] AS [Sgname], [w0].[FirstGroupId]
        FROM [WSProductSecondGroup] AS [w0]
        WHERE [w0].[IsRemoved] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [w].[PrdFirstGroupID] = [t].[FirstGroupId]
    WHERE [w].[IsRemoved] IS NULL
) AS [t0] ON [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId] = [t0].[ParsaPooladMenusId]
ORDER BY [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId], [t0].[PrdFirstGroupID], [t0].[WsproductSecondGroupId]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId], [p].[Name], [p].[UrlName], [p].[Image], [t0].[PrdFirstGroupID], [t0].[FGName], [t0].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t0].[Sgname]
FROM [ParsaPooladMenus] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [w].[PrdFirstGroupID], [w].[FGName], [t].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t].[Sgname], [w].[ParsaPooladMenusId]
    FROM [WSProductFirstGroup] AS [w]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID] AS [WsproductSecondGroupId], [w0].[SGName] AS [Sgname], [w0].[FirstGroupId]
        FROM [WSProductSecondGroup] AS [w0]
        WHERE [w0].[IsRemoved] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [w].[PrdFirstGroupID] = [t].[FirstGroupId]
    WHERE [w].[IsRemoved] IS NULL
) AS [t0] ON [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId] = [t0].[ParsaPooladMenusId]
ORDER BY [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId], [t0].[PrdFirstGroupID], [t0].[WsproductSecondGroupId]" (0723d8ff)

    FROM [dbo].[Blogs] AS [b1]
    WHERE [b1].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[BlogCategoryId]

    FROM [dbo].[Blogs] AS [b1]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[BlogCategoryId]

    FROM [dbo].[Blogs] AS [b1]
    WHERE [b1].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[BlogCategoryId]

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Author], [t].[BlogCategoryId], [t].[Body], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[InsertTime], [t].[IsRemoved], [t].[IsVerified], [t].[IsVideoClip], [t].[LocalTime], [t].[Position], [t].[RegisterUserId], [t].[RemoveTime], [t].[RequestToAuthorFav], [t].[Slug], [t].[SmallDescription], [t].[Title], [t].[UpdateTime], [t].[VideoClipDuration], [t].[VisitCount], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Color], [t0].[FaIcon], [t0].[ImageUrl], [t0].[InsertTime], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsRemoved], [t0].[LocalTime], [t0].[Name], [t0].[RegisterUserId], [t0].[RemoveTime], [t0].[Slug], [t0].[SmallDescription], [t0].[UpdateTime]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [b].[Id], [b].[Author], [b].[BlogCategoryId], [b].[Body], [b].[ImageUrl], [b].[InsertTime], [b].[IsRemoved], [b].[IsVerified], [b].[IsVideoClip], [b].[LocalTime], [b].[Position], [b].[RegisterUserId], [b].[RemoveTime], [b].[RequestToAuthorFav], [b].[Slug], [b].[SmallDescription], [b].[Title], [b].[UpdateTime], [b].[VideoClipDuration], [b].[VisitCount]
    FROM [dbo].[Blogs] AS [b]
    WHERE ((([b].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([b].[IsVerified] = CAST(1 AS bit))) AND ([b].[Position] = 0)) AND ([b].[RequestToAuthorFav] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
    ORDER BY [b].[Id] DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[Id], [b0].[Color], [b0].[FaIcon], [b0].[ImageUrl], [b0].[InsertTime], [b0].[IsActive], [b0].[IsRemoved], [b0].[LocalTime], [b0].[Name], [b0].[RegisterUserId], [b0].[RemoveTime], [b0].[Slug], [b0].[SmallDescription], [b0].[UpdateTime]
    FROM [dbo].[BlogCategories] AS [b0]
    WHERE [b0].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[BlogCategoryId] = [t0].[Id]

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Color], [t].[FaIcon], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[InsertTime], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsRemoved], [t].[LocalTime], [t].[Name], [t].[RegisterUserId], [t].[RemoveTime], [t].[Slug], [t].[SmallDescription], [t].[UpdateTime], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Author], [t0].[BlogCategoryId], [t0].[Body], [t0].[ImageUrl], [t0].[InsertTime], [t0].[IsRemoved], [t0].[IsVerified], [t0].[IsVideoClip], [t0].[LocalTime], [t0].[Position], [t0].[RegisterUserId], [t0].[RemoveTime], [t0].[RequestToAuthorFav], [t0].[Slug], [t0].[SmallDescription], [t0].[Title], [t0].[UpdateTime], [t0].[VideoClipDuration], [t0].[VisitCount]

    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [b0].[Id], [b0].[Color], [b0].[FaIcon], [b0].[ImageUrl], [b0].[InsertTime], [b0].[IsActive], [b0].[IsRemoved], [b0].[LocalTime], [b0].[Name], [b0].[RegisterUserId], [b0].[RemoveTime], [b0].[Slug], [b0].[SmallDescription], [b0].[UpdateTime], (

    FROM [dbo].[Blogs] AS [b1]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[BlogCategoryId]

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Color], [t].[FaIcon], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[InsertTime], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsRemoved], [t].[LocalTime], [t].[Name], [t].[RegisterUserId], [t].[RemoveTime], [t].[Slug], [t].[SmallDescription], [t].[UpdateTime], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Author], [t0].[BlogCategoryId], [t0].[Body], [t0].[ImageUrl], [t0].[InsertTime], [t0].[IsRemoved], [t0].[IsVerified], [t0].[IsVideoClip], [t0].[LocalTime], [t0].[Position], [t0].[RegisterUserId], [t0].[RemoveTime], [t0].[RequestToAuthorFav], [t0].[Slug], [t0].[SmallDescription], [t0].[Title], [t0].[UpdateTime], [t0].[VideoClipDuration], [t0].[VisitCount]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [b0].[Id], [b0].[Color], [b0].[FaIcon], [b0].[ImageUrl], [b0].[InsertTime], [b0].[IsActive], [b0].[IsRemoved], [b0].[LocalTime], [b0].[Name], [b0].[RegisterUserId], [b0].[RemoveTime], [b0].[Slug], [b0].[SmallDescription], [b0].[UpdateTime], (
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([b].[VisitCount]), 0)
        FROM [dbo].[Blogs] AS [b]
        WHERE ([b].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([b0].[Id] = [b].[BlogCategoryId])) AS [c]
    FROM [dbo].[BlogCategories] AS [b0]
    WHERE [b0].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
    ORDER BY (
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM([b].[VisitCount]), 0)
        FROM [dbo].[Blogs] AS [b]
        WHERE ([b].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([b0].[Id] = [b].[BlogCategoryId])) DESC
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b1].[Id], [b1].[Author], [b1].[BlogCategoryId], [b1].[Body], [b1].[ImageUrl], [b1].[InsertTime], [b1].[IsRemoved], [b1].[IsVerified], [b1].[IsVideoClip], [b1].[LocalTime], [b1].[Position], [b1].[RegisterUserId], [b1].[RemoveTime], [b1].[RequestToAuthorFav], [b1].[Slug], [b1].[SmallDescription], [b1].[Title], [b1].[UpdateTime], [b1].[VideoClipDuration], [b1].[VisitCount]
    FROM [dbo].[Blogs] AS [b1]
    WHERE [b1].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[BlogCategoryId]
ORDER BY [t].[c] DESC, [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b1].[Id], [b1].[Author], [b1].[BlogCategoryId], [b1].[Body], [b1].[ImageUrl], [b1].[InsertTime], [b1].[IsRemoved], [b1].[IsVerified], [b1].[IsVideoClip], [b1].[LocalTime], [b1].[Position], [b1].[RegisterUserId], [b1].[RemoveTime], [b1].[RequestToAuthorFav], [b1].[Slug], [b1].[SmallDescription], [b1].[Title], [b1].[UpdateTime], [b1].[VideoClipDuration], [b1].[VisitCount]
    FROM [dbo].[Blogs] AS [b1]
    WHERE [b1].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[BlogCategoryId]
ORDER BY [t].[c] DESC, [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Color], [t].[FaIcon], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[InsertTime], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsRemoved], [t].[LocalTime], [t].[Name], [t].[RegisterUserId], [t].[RemoveTime], [t].[Slug], [t].[SmallDescription], [t].[UpdateTime], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Author], [t0].[BlogCategoryId], [t0].[Body], [t0].[ImageUrl], [t0].[InsertTime], [t0].[IsRemoved], [t0].[IsVerified], [t0].[IsVideoClip], [t0].[LocalTime], [t0].[Position], [t0].[RegisterUserId], [t0].[RemoveTime], [t0].[RequestToAuthorFav], [t0].[Slug], [t0].[SmallDescription], [t0].[Title], [t0].[UpdateTime], [t0].[VideoClipDuration], [t0].[VisitCount]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b1].[Id], [b1].[Author], [b1].[BlogCategoryId], [b1].[Body], [b1].[ImageUrl], [b1].[InsertTime], [b1].[IsRemoved], [b1].[IsVerified], [b1].[IsVideoClip], [b1].[LocalTime], [b1].[Position], [b1].[RegisterUserId], [b1].[RemoveTime], [b1].[RequestToAuthorFav], [b1].[Slug], [b1].[SmallDescription], [b1].[Title], [b1].[UpdateTime], [b1].[VideoClipDuration], [b1].[VisitCount]
    FROM [dbo].[Blogs] AS [b1]
    WHERE [b1].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[BlogCategoryId]
ORDER BY [t].[c] DESC, [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId], [p].[Name], [p].[UrlName], [p].[Icon], [t0].[PrdFirstGroupID], [t0].[FGName], [t0].[EnFgname], [t0].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t0].[Sgname], [t0].[EnSgname]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [w].[PrdFirstGroupID], [w].[FGName], [w].[EnFgname], [t].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t].[Sgname], [t].[EnSgname], [w].[ParsaPooladMenusId]
    FROM [WSProductFirstGroup] AS [w]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID] AS [WsproductSecondGroupId], [w0].[SGName] AS [Sgname], REPLACE([w0].[EnSgname], N' ', N'-') AS [EnSgname], [w0].[FirstGroupId]

        WHERE [w0].[IsRemoved] IS NULL

    WHERE [w].[IsRemoved] IS NULL
) AS [t0] ON [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId] = [t0].[ParsaPooladMenusId]

    WHERE [b1].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[BlogCategoryId]

""SELECT [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId], [p].[Name], [p].[UrlName], [p].[Image], [t0].[PrdFirstGroupID], [t0].[FGName], [t0].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t0].[Sgname]
FROM [ParsaPooladMenus] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [w].[PrdFirstGroupID], [w].[FGName], [t].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t].[Sgname], [w].[ParsaPooladMenusId]
    FROM [WSProductFirstGroup] AS [w]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID] AS [WsproductSecondGroupId], [w0].[SGName] AS [Sgname], [w0].[FirstGroupId]
        FROM [WSProductSecondGroup] AS [w0]
        WHERE [w0].[IsRemoved] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [w].[PrdFirstGroupID] = [t].[FirstGroupId]
    WHERE [w].[IsRemoved] IS NULL
) AS [t0] ON [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId] = [t0].[ParsaPooladMenusId]
ORDER BY [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId], [t0].[PrdFirstGroupID], [t0].[WsproductSecondGroupId]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Color], [t].[FaIcon], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[InsertTime], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsRemoved], [t].[LocalTime], [t].[Name], [t].[RegisterUserId], [t].[RemoveTime], [t].[Slug], [t].[SmallDescription], [t].[UpdateTime], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Author], [t0].[BlogCategoryId], [t0].[Body], [t0].[ImageUrl], [t0].[InsertTime], [t0].[IsRemoved], [t0].[IsVerified], [t0].[IsVideoClip], [t0].[LocalTime], [t0].[Position], [t0].[RegisterUserId], [t0].[RemoveTime], [t0].[RequestToAuthorFav], [t0].[Slug], [t0].[SmallDescription], [t0].[Title], [t0].[UpdateTime], [t0].[VideoClipDuration], [t0].[VisitCount]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[BlogCategoryId]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [w].[PrdFirstGroupID], [w].[FGName], [w].[EnFgname], [t].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t].[Sgname], [t].[EnSgname], [w].[ParsaPooladMenusId]
    FROM [WSProductFirstGroup] AS [w]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID] AS [WsproductSecondGroupId], [w0].[SGName] AS [Sgname], REPLACE([w0].[EnSgname], N' ', N'-') AS [EnSgname], [w0].[FirstGroupId]

    FROM [WSProductFirstGroup] AS [w]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID] AS [WsproductSecondGroupId], [w0].[SGName] AS [Sgname], REPLACE([w0].[EnSgname], N' ', N'-') AS [EnSgname], [w0].[FirstGroupId]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b1].[Id], [b1].[Author], [b1].[BlogCategoryId], [b1].[Body], [b1].[ImageUrl], [b1].[InsertTime], [b1].[IsRemoved], [b1].[IsVerified], [b1].[IsVideoClip], [b1].[LocalTime], [b1].[Position], [b1].[RegisterUserId], [b1].[RemoveTime], [b1].[RequestToAuthorFav], [b1].[Slug], [b1].[SmallDescription], [b1].[Title], [b1].[UpdateTime], [b1].[VideoClipDuration], [b1].[VisitCount]
    FROM [dbo].[Blogs] AS [b1]
    WHERE [b1].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[BlogCategoryId]
ORDER BY [t].[c] DESC, [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [b].[Id], [b].[BuyerId], [b].[InsertTime], [b].[IsRemoved], [b].[RemoveTime], [b].[UpdateTime]
    FROM [dbo].[Baskets] AS [b]
    WHERE ([b].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)) AND ([b].[BuyerId] = @__userId_0)
) AS [t]

    SELECT [b0].[Id], [b0].[BasketId], [b0].[InsertTime], [b0].[IsRemoved], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Quantity], [b0].[RemoveTime], [b0].[UnitPrice], [b0].[UpdateTime], [t0].[Id] AS [Id0], [t0].[AppType], [t0].[FirstRegisterDate], [t0].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [t0].[FirstRegisterUserId], [t0].[Fpid], [t0].[Guid], [t0].[InsertTime] AS [InsertTime0], [t0].[IsRemoved] AS [IsRemoved0], [t0].[LanguageId], [t0].[LocalTime], [t0].[Month1], [t0].[OrderView], [t0].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [t0].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [t0].[PrdBarCode], [t0].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [t0].[PrdCode], [t0].[PrdColorId], [t0].[PrdCommissionDisable], [t0].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [t0].[PrdCrmId], [t0].[PrdDescription], [t0].[PrdDesign], [t0].[PrdFirstBarcode], [t0].[PrdFirstSerial], [t0].[PrdGroupId], [t0].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [t0].[PrdInactiveInSale], [t0].[PrdLatinName], [t0].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [t0].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [t0].[PrdMaxQty], [t0].[PrdMinQty], [t0].[PrdModel], [t0].[PrdName], [t0].[PrdPrice], [t0].[PrdSecondBarcode], [t0].[PrdSecondSerial], [t0].[PrdShpcode], [t0].[PrdShpdescription], [t0].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [t0].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [t0].[PrdShpisActive], [t0].[PrdShpmodel], [t0].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [t0].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [t0].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [t0].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [t0].[PrdShptitle], [t0].[PrdSize], [t0].[PrdSleepDay], [t0].[PrdThirdBarcode], [t0].[PrdThirdSerial], [t0].[PrdType], [t0].[PrdUnitId], [t0].[RegisterDate], [t0].[RegisterDatePersian], [t0].[RemoveTime] AS [RemoveTime0], [t0].[UpdateTime] AS [UpdateTime0], [t0].[UserId], [t0].[VisitCount]
    FROM [dbo].[BasketItems] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[AppType], [p].[FirstRegisterDate], [p].[FirstRegisterDatePersian], [p].[FirstRegisterUserId], [p].[Fpid], [p].[Guid], [p].[InsertTime], [p].[IsRemoved], [p].[LanguageId], [p].[LocalTime], [p].[Month1], [p].[OrderView], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoCharBarcode], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdAutoNumBarcode], [p].[PrdBarCode], [p].[PrdBarCodeTypeId], [p].[PrdCode], [p].[PrdColorId], [p].[PrdCommissionDisable], [p].[PrdCommissionPercentRate], [p].[PrdCrmId], [p].[PrdDescription], [p].[PrdDesign], [p].[PrdFirstBarcode], [p].[PrdFirstSerial], [p].[PrdGroupId], [p].[PrdInactiveInBuy], [p].[PrdInactiveInSale], [p].[PrdLatinName], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdCode], [p].[PrdLinkAccPrdId], [p].[PrdMaxQty], [p].[PrdMinQty], [p].[PrdModel], [p].[PrdName], [p].[PrdPrice], [p].[PrdSecondBarcode], [p].[PrdSecondSerial], [p].[PrdShpcode], [p].[PrdShpdescription], [p].[PrdShpdescriptionIi], [p].[PrdShphiddenPriceInNoStock], [p].[PrdShpisActive], [p].[PrdShpmodel], [p].[PrdShpotherSupplierId], [p].[PrdShpselfSupplier], [p].[PrdShpstockManageTypeId], [p].[PrdShpstockManualyCount], [p].[PrdShptitle], [p].[PrdSize], [p].[PrdSleepDay], [p].[PrdThirdBarcode], [p].[PrdThirdSerial], [p].[PrdType], [p].[PrdUnitId], [p].[RegisterDate], [p].[RegisterDatePersian], [p].[RemoveTime], [p].[UpdateTime], [p].[UserId], [p].[VisitCount]
        FROM [dbo].[Products] AS [p]
        WHERE [p].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
    ) AS [t0] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [t0].[Id]
    WHERE [b0].[IsRemoved] <> CAST(1 AS bit)
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[BasketId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId], [p].[Name], [p].[UrlName], [p].[Icon], [t0].[PrdFirstGroupID], [t0].[FGName], [t0].[EnFgname], [t0].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t0].[Sgname], [t0].[EnSgname]
FROM [ParsaPooladMenus] AS [p]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [w].[PrdFirstGroupID], [w].[FGName], [w].[EnFgname], [t].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t].[Sgname], [t].[EnSgname], [w].[ParsaPooladMenusId]
    FROM [WSProductFirstGroup] AS [w]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID] AS [WsproductSecondGroupId], [w0].[SGName] AS [Sgname], REPLACE([w0].[EnSgname], N' ', N'-') AS [EnSgname], [w0].[FirstGroupId]
        FROM [WSProductSecondGroup] AS [w0]
        WHERE [w0].[IsRemoved] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [w].[PrdFirstGroupID] = [t].[FirstGroupId]
    WHERE [w].[IsRemoved] IS NULL
) AS [t0] ON [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId] = [t0].[ParsaPooladMenusId]
ORDER BY [p].[ParsaPooladMenusId], [t0].[PrdFirstGroupID], [t0].[WsproductSecondGroupId]" (0723d8ff)
